packages.description:
AWS SDK for Ruby V1
Version 1 of the AWS SDK for Ruby. Available as both `aws-sdk` and `aws-sdk-v1`.
Use `aws-sdk-v1` if you want to load v1 and v2 of the Ruby SDK in the same
application.
